      <div class="mb-5">
      <text class="text-lg">
        From childhood, my world has been shaped by a fascination with creation. At 10, I began teaching myself how to code. 
        By 15, I was already contributing to the blockchain field professionally. 
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-5">
      <text class="text-lg">
        Over the years, I've thrived in various startups and have dedicated myself to crafting open source tools that empower developers 
        and bolster community. At the heart of my journey is a drive to build tools that connect people and elevate collective potential. 
      </text>
    </div>
    <div>
      <text class="text-lg">
        <b>As I continue on this path, I remain true to my childhood dream, channeling my passion into every line of code and community endeavor. </b>
      </text>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="https://twitter.com/jetjadeja" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-2">Recent Projects {"</>"}</div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="Demo Project 1"
